---
title: Beef Brisket Lasagne with Rocket Salad & Parmesan
description: A lasagne is one of those dishes you can dress up or down so let’s make it the star of this luxurious dinner show. There are
plenty of veggie accessories to add to the tender beef brisket filling, spiced and seasoned with notes of mushroom and
garlic. A bechamel sauce with Parmesan ties it together to create layers of deliciousness that will take your breath away.
